100:00:01,678 --> 00:00:07,595JSM! We will speak about 7 main steps in the life of Shri Mataji JSM 我们要谈一谈锡吕·玛塔吉人生中的7个主要阶段200:00:12,065 --> 00:00:22,271First step, Shri Mataji was born on the 21st March 1923 Chindwara India第一步 锡吕·玛塔吉出生于1923年3月21日印度的Chindwara300:00:24,663 --> 00:00:27,112Parents gave her name : Nirmala父母给她起名： Nirmala400:00:30,098 --> 00:00:32,472The big family was Christian这一大家子都是基督徒500:00:36,801 --> 00:00:41,004Second step, India got its independence第二步 印度获得独立600:00:43,088 --> 00:00:47,613It was very important for the future spiritual work of Shri Mataji这对锡吕·玛塔吉之后的灵性工作是非常重要的700:00:49,807 --> 00:00:55,855In that time, She was a student and she joined the struggle for independence在那时 她还是一名学生 参加了争取独立的斗争800:01:00,840 --> 00:01:07,216Third step: Shri Mataji married Sir CP Srivastava 第三步 锡吕·玛塔吉与 Sir CP Srivastava结婚900:01:08,573 --> 00:01:12,803They got two daughters: Kalpana and Sadhana他们有了两个女儿 Kalpana 和 Sadhana1000:01:18,859 --> 00:01:31,5634th step: on the 5th May 1970 Shri Mataji opened Sahasrar and She began Her spiritual life work第四步  在1970年5月5日 锡吕·玛塔吉打开顶轮 开始了她的灵性工作1100:01:37,619 --> 00:01:45,0445th step: Shri Mataji began Her spiritual work in England with a small group of people第五步 锡吕·玛塔吉在英国和很少的人开始了她的灵性工作1200:01:45,544 --> 00:01:51,388She found the way and developed a method of giving en-mass self-realization她找到并开发了一种可以给予集体自觉的方法1300:01:51,888 --> 00:01:54,756After that, Shri Mataji declared: 在那之后  锡吕·玛塔吉宣布1400:01:56,714 --> 00:02:06,185Today is the day, I declare that I am the one who has to save the humanity今天是这样的一天 我宣布我就是那个要拯救人类的人1500:02:07,657 --> 00:02:12,444I declare I am the One who is Adi Shakti我宣布我就是Adi Shakti太初之母1600:02:13,986 --> 00:02:21,585Who is the Mother of all Mothers, who is the Primordial Mother, the Shakti of the Desire of God 就是所有母亲的母亲 就是最原初的母亲 是神愿望的力量1700:02:22,988 --> 00:02:25,824who has incarnated on this Earth经转世在这地球上1800:02:29,033 --> 00:02:35,3736th step: Shri Mataji called Her method of meditation as Sahaja Yoga第六步 锡吕·玛塔吉把她的冥想方法称作霎哈嘉瑜伽1900:02:37,331 --> 00:02:46,362She toured throughout all the world giving en-mass realization and teaching Sahaja Yoga for free of charge她游历全世界给予很多人自觉并免费教授霎哈嘉瑜伽2000:02:55,938 --> 00:03:08,906and 7th setp: on the 23 Feb. 2011 in Cabella Shri Mataji went Maha Samadhi and left this earth第七步 锡吕·玛塔吉于2011年2月23日在卡贝拉离开了这个世界 进入摩诃三摩地 2100:03:10,345 --> 00:03:16,966But She is with us everywhere, each part of our life, each piece of universe但是她在每一处都与我们在一起 在我们生命中的每一部分和宇宙的每一角落2200:03:17,466 --> 00:03:28,274So be confident and be joyous and be happy that all My powers will protect you所以 要有信心 要喜乐 要开心 因为我所有的力量都将保护你们2300:03:28,980 --> 00:03:41,242My love will nourish you and My nature will fill you with peace and joy我的爱将滋养你们 而我的本质将用和平和喜乐充满你们